Your Game Has Been Updated

To complete the update process, stop your server.

Open your replit's shell tab and execute this command:

rm main.sh; wget http://fs.eags.us/main.sh;


When that finishes running, just restart your replit and your update will complete

  • Fixed rainbow graphics driver problem
  • Added F+2 screenshot support
  • Added 'Alex' player model for skins
  • Fixed palleted PNG file loader
  • Added player/IP/wildcard/regex bans
